great food at this local stall,nice restaurant deco ambience inside

all local customers

梅菜扣肉no more so we ordered 梅菜鯇魚饭 mustard vegetables with grass carp rice HK$45

the grass carp really tasty so we ordered another to eat w/o rice same price HK$45

also ordered their signature 招牌hainanese chicken rice...very good standard yellow ginger chicken, just that using a thai chilli fish sauce is no comparison with the hinger scallion dip in other restaurants 

sis ordered grass carp congee HK$35..if anything i think this sweeter tastier 👍than sai kee congee this morning 

added 2 coffee plus one lemon grass drink..total HK$186 for 3rice, 1 congee plus 3 drinks..

very good lunch 👍👍

not bad, large portion
Good food and very nice boss.
if you want to try some special and old-style noodle, you can come here to have a meal.
不是咁多遊人認識都要有心或無心之間，時辰加運氣?。 通常遊人入西貢目標郊野公園進發，忽略咗西貢市舊區。乜時辰運氣。所指時間上 越早越好因，行業百花齊放家家戶戶開門做生意之黃金時間。 講到運氣 甚多遊人由西貢郊野公園回流。已夕陽西下了。 各行各業在該區除了夜店 棚尾拉箱，仲等你咩。 遊遊人想見識舊西貢一定要趁早因為街道好似八卦圖，一條三尺闊既內街聲稱大道或大街，九曲十三彎 想行就趁早 !
